features: 【Dual Head Modern Design】The blue table lamp adopts a double-head design.The left and right head can be unfolded into a straight line, with the 160-degree swing angle in up and down direction, providing you with a larger lighting coverage and angle. Foldable design makes it effectively reduce writing shadows.

【3 Lighting Modes and Stepless Dimmable】With a sensitive touch switch, you can freely switch 3 lighting modes--warm white, natural white and cold white. In each mode, the brightness can be adjusted to suit your various lighting needs. Besides, the brightness can be remembered when you choose this mode again, which can save your time to adjust the brightness one more time.

【Rechargeable Battery Operated Desk Lamp 】Built in high quality 2000mAh battery, you can take your table lamp to anywhere you need the light. It can last Max 15 hours lighting in lowest brightness. It comes in 32 inch USB cable (AC Adapter is not included), can be powered by USB Charger, Computer, Power bank, Phone Adapter, etc. You can use anytime, anywhere.

【Eye Protection Portable Study Lamp】Small Desk Lamp double-swing-arm lamp has high quality 32 LEDs to offer flicker-free, non-shadow, flicker-free, uniform lighting. Perfect for working, reading, study, webcam Zoom and soft light allows you to read in bed without disturbing others.

【Safe and Reliable After-sales Service】LuxLumin LED desk light is using fire-resistant ABS material and it is safe and cool to touch after extensive use. We offer 12 months warranty and we welcome any emails or messages about our desk lamp. We will provide our professional answer in 24/7 to make you satisfied and happy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for a kid's desk
reviews.reviewText: This lamp is lightweight plastic, and would be perfect for a kid's desk. It's perfect for my needs, too. I work from home and my workspace gets very dark when the sun goes down. I keep it plugged into a USB port all day and use it for about 2 hours before the workday is over. After work, I move it to the hallway between my bedroom and bathroom, which is also very dark at night. It keeps the hallway illuminated all night on a charge. I also like that it has 4 different brightness levels. The only thing I don't like is that when I'm not using it and I fold it flat, the top touches the switch and it turns itself on. That's a minor inconvenience, though. I would definitely buy this lamp again.
